  "bodyHtml": "<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Танд&nbsp;<span id=\"MathJax-Span-3\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">5</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-4\" style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-5\" style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-6\" style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">х</span></span></span></span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-7\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">5</span>&nbsp;матриц өгөгдсөн бөгөөд энэ нь&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">24</span>&nbsp;ширхэг&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">0,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">1</span>&nbsp;ширхэг&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">1-</span>ийн тооноос бүтсэн. Матрицын мөрийг дээрээс нь доош нь&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">1-</span>ээс&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">